{"tid":195508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半年鑑定5萬部A片　「鑑黃師」警察視力下滑","createTime":"2017-04-10T15:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T18:07:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8280ebc51774486b0d149d899d661a3a8fe488f","tid":195508,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"2017/04/09<br />\n大陸有一批警察的工作是鑑定A片，被稱為「鑑黃師」。別以為專門「看片」的工作很輕鬆，要擔任這項工作必須符合45歲以上、已婚、心理素質極佳等要求，有人長期下來視力下滑。<br />\n<br />\n直播,性侵,強暴,影片,A片▲圖／達志影像 ID-498622<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/04/15/498622-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F04%2F15%2F498622-XXL.jpg&h=4516fc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／達志影像<br />\n<br />\n揚子晚報網今天報導，鑑黃師工作門檻很高，必須已婚、年滿45歲以上、心理素質極佳、能熟悉掌握法律及相關知識的大陸一線民警。目前，江蘇省如皋市公安局僅有3名民警經嚴格培訓後持有鑑黃工作證。<br />\n<br />\n2007年，當時46歲的顧維宏為了案件審理需要，被調到這個職位，一做就是10年。顧維宏說，做這工作要熟記關於淫穢及色情出版物的各項法律規定，只要符合其中一條，就算是淫穢物品。<br />\n<br />\n顧維宏表示，長時間看影片對眼睛的傷害很大，自己的視力已明顯下滑。此外，因為辦案時間有嚴格規定，一接到鑑定委託就得立刻「投入工作」。曾半年內和其他6名同事分工看完5萬部A片，熬夜是常有的事情。<br />\n<br />\n顧維宏說，近年來，傳播淫穢物品手段也越來越隱蔽，很多淫穢影片夾雜在電視或電影的故事情節中，增加了鑑定的難度與工作量。他們需要對平均時長超過50分鐘的影片從頭看到尾、不能快轉，工作量之大可想而知。<br />\n<br />\n談到這份工作，顧維宏直言，最初難免有些難為情，不好意思對朋友說自己負責的業務。他說，當面對工作時，腦子裡想的只有淫穢色情的標準。而隨著傳播載具的進步，他也要學習克服各種「技術難題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=241536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D241536&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f7213922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D241536&h=f5710d95\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=241536</a>"},{"pid":"5d338716586b7c798908f2bdd1ec4548eabfcd93","tid":195508,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U869672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU869672.jpg&h=eb0ac273&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11d3f466f984cea4a2d15e2a5dbff091dbe19631","tid":195508,"uid":76637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U869672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU869672.jpg&h=eb0ac273&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39355650dd4246936143734dca2afb41b23ee1e","tid":195508,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U869672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU869672.jpg&h=eb0ac273&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041d568b7f9a4c9974c21d3e408618647a6c7c43","tid":195508,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U869672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU869672.jpg&h=eb0ac273&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcec4d47460ec6cc26aba6d5fe7823e43756e961","tid":195508,"uid":16885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"